-- Bahrain's GIB plans 2 bln Saudi riyal note issue
-- By Azza Al Arabi
-- Sun Apr 20, 2014 08:19AM EDT
-- None



DUBAI, April 20 (Reuters) - Bahrain's Gulf International Bank [GLFBK.UL] plans to issue a 2 billion-riyal ($545 million) floating rate notes with a lifespan of five years through a private placement in Saudi Arabia, a prospectus showed on Sunday.

